{"type":null,"faqId":38502,"title":"手机找回","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{color:blue;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125472\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在使用手机找回功能前，请确保手机处于联网状态。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 华为云服务”。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“手机找回”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“开启手机找回”开关，开启手机找回。开启后，即可通过电脑登录 </span><a href=\"https://www1.hicloud.com%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">www.hicloud.com</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> 进行如下操作：</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">  </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">对遗失的手机进行定位。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">  </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">给手机发送信息。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">  </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">远程锁定遗失的手机。锁定后，您的手机需要输入密码后才能使用。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">  </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">备份或清除手机上的数据以免重要数据丢失或泄露。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":1070,"faqType":"华为云应用","useful":4,"unUseful":6,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3782","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hicloud","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448685000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":693,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":4,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"手机找回","avgScore":4.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}